Subject: Fan Hub Removal

I don't know about Vanagons, but on my 74 that hub is press fit onto a the
tapered end of the crankshaft with a woodruff key to index it. Those babies
are on TIGHT, so I usually use a three-jaw puller to get it off. Of course,
YMMV.

Hope this helps,
Dave

